data.description: This one-of-a-kind custom built home sits on a large, quiet corner lot. Stepping into the home you are greeted by a Mediterranean style great room, complete with a wood-beamed cathedral ceiling, indoor fountain, a beautiful bricked wall that includes a fireplace and built-in shelving, wrought-iron railings, arched doorways and tiled floors. The functional kitchen has ample storage, plenty of natural light and beautiful brick work. The dining room has a pass-through to the kitchen and a built-in hutch. The primary suite is isolated from the guest bedrooms and all the bedrooms have walk-in closets and en suite bathrooms. The spacious laundry room has a sink, closet, and room for a freezer. The amazing basement in this home is like taking a step back in time! A custom-made bar w/a fridge, a pool table, and a wall-mounted TV all convey! The 3-car over-sized garage has a large storage room. The backyard fencing is cinder block and metal. Lots Of Storage In This Home, Come See For Yourself!
